				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You could use TGROM (Mega Man 4, Mega Man 6, Ninja Crusaders), or a TLROM board modded to behave like TGROM. Or you could use TGROM modded to take a 62256 (32 KiB SRAM), which allows both tile animation and arbitrary updating.<br /><br />But what in your project needs MMC3? Could it get away with something simpler like BNROM (Deadly Towers, Haunted Halloween '85) or MMC1 SGROM/SNROM (too many to list)?</div>

